{
  "texts": [
    "Aiming for consistency in distribution between test and training data, if the number of the used tables falls below 𝑡𝑜𝑝 𝑘1, we incorporate randomly selected, unused tables from the database as padding.",
    "A similar procedure is adopted for columns, ensuring each retained table contains 𝑡𝑜𝑝 𝑘2 columns.",
    "The integration of the schema filter not only reduces the length of the database prompts but also alleviates the schema-linking pressure for the model.",
    "Value RetrieverRetrieving values from the database that align with the question can help the language model perform better schema linking when generating predicates.",
    "For a natural language question in the BIRD benchmark \"How many clients opened their accounts in Jesenik branch were women?"
  ]
}